{"tid":801940,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一句微信群中「習豬頭最近怎麼樣啊？好長時間沒看新聞聯播了」。拘留，罰款。","createTime":"2018-09-01T05:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T09:05:29.000Z","uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0437802cf3b6917d62713d05cf036d9a26ea2a","tid":801940,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dl5eZ0_UcAAXKdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDl5eZ0_UcAAXKdv.jpg&h=36635905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1035368777045536768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1035368777045536768&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2f33b213\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FpZO5xK2Su74DiBW%2Fstatus%2F1035368777045536768&h=c00a5c6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pZO5xK2Su74DiBW/status/1035368777045536768</a>"},{"pid":"0fe644a2040397b5729cf1e616eb8e1a815b4c76","tid":801940,"uid":42820,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/01/132716_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F01%2F132716_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=187f81f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdf4133ad62ad990347d7db008abca539829cbe2","tid":801940,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1d2db11c8244845b70490ae97b7962932cd51e","tid":801940,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"冇槍斃 已經係人權重大突破"},{"pid":"55bc91fdf09ff754a0b03d39703d1cf94dd78e68","tid":801940,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:02:14.000Z","msg":"【現代文字獄】「習豬頭最近怎麼樣」 網民被行拘10天<br />\n<br />\n61,250<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0901 18:46<br />\n 網民在微信群組發出「習豬頭最近怎麼樣」，被罰行拘10天。(互聯網)<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n網民在微信群組發出「習豬頭最近怎麼樣」，被罰行拘10天。(互聯網)<br />\n海南三亞市天涯區水蛟村一名網民，7月19日在微信群組發言「習豬頭最近怎麼樣了，好幾年沒看新聞聯播了」，1個月後被當地公安機關傳喚接受調查，並處以行政拘留10日，罰款500元人民幣（約574港元）。<br />\n<br />\n根據三亞市公安局天涯分局行政處罰決定書顯示，被告倪華平（39歲），初中教育程度，於7月19日晚上9時33分在三亞市水蛟村對面出租屋內休息時，因自己覺得社會不公平，使用手機微信在一個名叫「邵陽被販小孩尋親團」的群組發出一句：「習豬頭最近怎麼樣了，好幾年沒看新聞聯播了」，以此來發洩內心的不滿。"},{"pid":"9baaf88c72c6b3fcb470b4853ec75400a3e3b881","tid":801940,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"直至上月20日中午12時20分許，倪華平在出租屋內被警方傳召到公安機關接受調。經查問，倪承認公然侮辱他人，根據《中華人民共和國治安管理處罰法》第四十二條第二項規定，對倪華平處以行拘並罰款。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58633763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58633763&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=59800924\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58633763&h=ae689e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58633763</a>"},{"pid":"0eb0950439fd992aa3e1fcc10a6371620849285f","tid":801940,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"大陸真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白色恐佈"},{"pid":"3bd3d7b18303d1b247e58229d2f91619f4de75a5","tid":801940,"uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"我唔知習豬頭係侮辱緊邊個WO,<br />\n既然D公安話佢係侮辱他人,請拿出證據證明畀人知佢侮辱緊邊個"},{"pid":"d8af86eeb4938d79a9a02cc6307e22aa475b5a23","tid":801940,"uid":59684,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"reply